# 安装 & 使用[Redis推荐Linux开发]
## 基于Homebrew安装Redis

brew -- version      //检查电脑上有没有安装Homebrew
brew search redis    //查看redis版本
brew install redis   //安装最新版本的redis

## 启动Redis
brew services start redis   //启动redis服务
brew services list    //查看mac上所有服务目前的状况
brew services stop redis      //关闭redis
brew services restart redis   //重启redis
redis-cli           //打开图形化界面
brew list redis     //查看redis安装的位置  //redis.conf的目录：/opt/homebrew/Cellar/redis/7.0.10/.bottle/etc/
